title: Lego Paradisa Sand Dollar Cafe 6411
features: The bar inside the café has two taps, a stove with a frying pan and a coffee machine. In front of the café is a small table with two seats and a sunshade and a sunlounger
Next to the lifeguard tower is a sign with the Coast Guard logo.
The included beach baseplate is unique to this set.
description: 6411 Sand Dollar Cafe is a Paradisa set released in 1992. It consists of a beach with a café, a small lifeguard tower, an ice cream cart, a sail board,a bicycle and five minifigures. These figures included a cook and a lifeguard.
